    <item>
      <title>普华永道调查显示，英国高管热衷于收购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/uk-s-top-bosses-are-keen-to-make-acquisitions-pwc-survey-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[四大会计师事务所之一的一项调查显示，随着利率稳定，英国的交易低迷应该会有所缓解，超过一半的英国首席执行官预计在未来三年内进行重大收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/uk-s-top-bosses-are-keen-to-make-acquisitions-pwc-survey-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰将第四个月保持利率稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/poland-to-keep-rates-steady-as-risks-are-weighed-decision-guide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着市场和政策制定者权衡通胀风险是否需要结束货币宽松周期，波兰央行将连续第四个月保持借贷成本不变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/poland-to-keep-rates-steady-as-risks-are-weighed-decision-guide</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
